lo que yo crea, Scully.

41
00:04:54,884 --> 00:04:56,432
Es importante lo que ellos creen.

42
00:04:56,552 --> 00:04:57,552
Los testigos auditivos.

43
00:04:57,672 --> 00:04:59,101
